&lt;h4 class=&quot;heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-GBI4dbbNboFMicxdJGWcltfonId&quot;&gt;About the Role&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XA1ndSqKroNyqbxfi2gcDeq2nXt&quot;&gt;We are looking for a strong &lt;strong&gt;Machine Learning Engineer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; / &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Computer Vision&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; to work on &lt;strong&gt;Traffic Sign Recognition&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; (&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TSR&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;) 2D detection&lt;/strong&gt; for production autonomous driving systems.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Ng3Zd17QLofdlLxZO3UcihX9nJe&quot;&gt;In this role, you will be responsible for the full lifecycle of TSR model development, including &lt;strong&gt;scenario analysis, data preparation, model training, evaluation, &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;optimization&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;, quantization, and deployment&lt;/strong&gt;. You will work closely with perception, data, infrastructure, and deployment teams to improve traffic sign detection performance across diverse real-world driving scenarios.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UTROdsl4pol0Ehx2vpccK976nre&quot;&gt;This role is ideal for candidates who enjoy solving practical computer vision problems, building reliable model iteration pipelines, and bringing perception models from offline training to onboard production systems.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-FY8ldvRXEopHagxseeuctxC4nTd&quot;&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/h4&gt;
