&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PjZLdAB2VoLjTox6xA8c5vpgnUg&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Develop and improve &lt;strong&gt;2D traffic sign detection models&lt;/strong&gt; for autonomous driving perception systems.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-NqBRd3SgQoM3BKx8WTCcl8ebnVd&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Analyze TSR-related scenarios and failure cases, including missed detections, false positives, occlusions, small objects, rare signs, region-specific signs, and adverse weather or lighting conditions.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BdOOddv45o1aJPxFALKcYsHjncg&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Prepare, clean, curate, and analyze training and evaluation datasets for TSR model iteration.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Uv7ydCzmJoWtszxZc8pcuRYLnBg&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
